gw.api.matter

Class MatterAssignmentPopup

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.assignment.AssignmentPopup
      • gw.api.assignment.CCAssignmentPopup
        • gw.api.matter.MatterAssignmentPopup

  • public class MatterAssignmentPopup
extends CCAssignmentPopup
    Wrapper object for assign matters UI screen. Stores user's selection of who or what matters should be assigned to. Also contains search criteria for user/group/queue search.
